'''恐龙皮肤'''目前已發現許多[[獸腳亞目|獸腳亞目]]恐龍具有[[羽毛|羽毛]]，包含：[[鳥面龍_(蒙古)|鳥面龍]]、[[中華龍鳥|中華龍鳥]]、[[帝龍|帝龍]]<ref name="SchweitzerWattEtAl1999FeatherlikeStructuresOfShuvuuia">{{en}}{{cite journal |author=Schweitzer, M.H., J.A. Watt, R. Avci, L. Knapp, L. Chiappe, M. Norell and M. Marshall. |date=July 1999 |title=Beta-keratin specific immunological reactivity in feather-like structures of the Cretaceous alvarezsaurid, ''Shuvuuia deserti'' |journal=Journal of Experimental Zoology (Mol Dev Evol) |volume=285 |issue=2 |pages=146–157 |doi=10.1002/(SICI)1097-010X(19990815)285:2<146::AID-JEZ7>3.0.CO;2-A |url=http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/cgi-bin/abstract/63000744/ABSTRACT |format=abstract page |access-date=2010-12-27 |archive-date=2012-12-10 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20121210052218/http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/cgi-bin/abstract/63000744/ABSTRACT |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="CurrieChen2001AnatomyOfSinosauropteryx">{{en}}{{cite journal |author=Currie, P.J., and Chen, P-j. |title=Anatomy of ''Sinosauropteryx prima'' from Liaoning, northeastern China |journal=Canadian Journal of Earth Sciences |volume=38 |issue=12 |date=December 2001 |pages=1705–1727 |url=http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/nrc/cjes/2001/00000038/00000012/art00008 |doi=10.1139/cjes-38-12-1705 |access-date=2010-12-27 |archive-date=2016-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818083606/http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/nrc/cjes/2001/00000038/00000012/art00008 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="XuNorellEtAlBasalTyrannosauroidsFromChina">{{en}}{{cite journal|author=Xu X.; Norell, M.A.; Kuang X.; Wang X.; Zhao Q.; and Jia C.|title=Basal tyrannosauroids from China and evidence for protofeathers in tyrannosauroids|journal=Nature|date=2004|volume=431|issue=7009|pages=680–684|pmid=15470426|doi=10.1038/nature02855|url=http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v431/n7009/abs/nature02855.html|format=abstract page|access-date=2010-12-27|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305154108/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v431/n7009/abs/nature02855.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另一群大型的獸腳類恐龍，[[鐮刀龍超科|鐮刀龍超科]]，可能也具有羽毛；其中的[[北票龍|北票龍]]似乎具有絨羽。但恐龍的羽毛痕跡大多發現於[[虛骨龍類|虛骨龍類]]）之中，所以無法從羽毛得知其他恐龍演化支的身體機能，例如：[[腔骨龍科|腔骨龍科]]、[[角鼻龍下目|角鼻龍下目]]、[[肉食龍下目|肉食龍下目]]、[[蜥腳下目|蜥腳下目]]、與[[鳥臀目|鳥臀目]]。從[[阿貝力龍科|阿貝力龍科]]的[[食肉牛龍|食肉牛龍]]的化石化皮膚顯示，該種恐龍並沒有覆蓋者羽毛，而是類似蜥蜴，上有多排瘤狀物<ref name="BonaparteNovasCoria1990Carnotaurus">{{en}}{{cite journal |author=Bonaparte, J.F., Novas, E.E., and Coria, R.A. |date=1990 |title=''Carnotaurus sastrei'' Bonaparte, the horned, lightly built carnosaur from the Middle Cretaceous of Patagonia |journal=Natural History Museum of Los Angeles County Contributions in Science |volume=416 |pages=1–42 |url=http://dinosaurs.nhm.org/staff/coriaworks.htm |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080510084320/http://dinosaurs.nhm.org/staff/coriaworks.htm |archivedate=2008-05-10 }}</ref>。成年食肉牛龍的體重約一公噸，體重大於或等於食肉牛龍的哺乳類，身上不是光滑的皮膚，就是很短的毛髮。因此無法從食肉牛龍得知較小的非虛骨龍類恐龍是否具有羽毛。

[[蜥腳下目|蜥腳下目]]中的[[畸形龍|畸形龍]]與某些物種的皮膚痕跡，已發現六角型的鱗片。而部份蜥腳類恐龍則具有骨板，例如[[薩爾塔龍|薩爾塔龍]]<ref>{{en}}{{ citation |author=Czerkas, S. A.  |date=1994 | contribution=The history and interpretation of sauropod skin impressions |title=Aspects of Sauropod Paleobiology | editor=Lockley, M.G., dos Santos, V.F., Meyer, C.A., and Hunt, A.P. | journal=Gaia |volume=10 |location=Lisbon, Portugal }}</ref>。[[角龍下目|角龍下目]]的[[三角龍|三角龍]]，具有大型的六角型鱗片，有時散佈者圓形鱗片<ref name="DodsonBarlowe1996Horned Dinosaurs">{{en}}{{cite book |author=Dodson, P., and Barlowe, W.D. |title=The Horned Dinosaurs: A Natural History |date=1996 |publisher=Princeton University Press |isbn=0691059004 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=NsBhg_H5FEwC&pg=PA31&lpg=PA31&dq=%22ceratopsian%22+skin&source=web&ots=0vLf_NLNPH&sig=TgsKlsc0tvbkbXfnlIEfe3SohkI&hl=en |access-date=2010-12-27 |archive-date=2021-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318164740/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=NsBhg_H5FEwC&pg=PA31&lpg=PA31&dq=%22ceratopsian%22+skin&source=web&ots=0vLf_NLNPH&sig=TgsKlsc0tvbkbXfnlIEfe3SohkI&hl=en |dead-url=no }} See also image at {{cite web |url=http://piclib.nhm.ac.uk/piclib/www/image.php?img=96447&frm=ser&search=cat_4 |title=Ceratopsian skin |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203051057/http://piclib.nhm.ac.uk/piclib/www/image.php?img=96447&frm=ser&search=cat_4 |archivedate=2014-02-03 }}</ref>。[[鴨嘴龍科|鴨嘴龍科]]的一些[[木乃伊|木乃伊]]化標本，也覆蓋者鱗片。[[包頭龍|包頭龍]]等[[甲龍科|甲龍科]]恐龍，身體覆蓋者骨質鱗甲與骨板，不太可能具有羽毛等覆蓋物<ref name="NewScientistBulletproofArmour">{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn6674-dinosaurs-bulletproof-armour-revealed.html |title=Dinosaurs' "bulletproof" armour revealed |date=16 November 2004 |publisher=NewScientist.com news service |author=Gosline, A. |access-date=2010-12-27 |archive-date=2015-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150122032507/http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn6674-dinosaurs-bulletproof-armour-revealed.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。相同地，[[劍龍類|劍龍類]]也不太可能具有羽毛覆蓋物，牠們可能利用背部的角板來調節體溫。

